scenes.description: Nerissa Ravencroft performing her song 'In My Feelings'.
Instrumental outro of the song with audience applause.
Audience chanting for an encore, led by a Jailbird mascot.
Nerissa returns to the stage for an MC segment, reflecting on the event.
Nerissa introduces her new merchandise, the Paper Knife.
Nerissa introduces her first EP 'In My Feelings'.
